title: F.A. Cup Highlights 2014-02-15 720p 50fps HDTV-wAm.mkv
description:
SPORT: FA Cup Highlights
On: itv Central HD
Date: Saturday 15th February 2014
Matt Smith is joined by Andy Townsend for highlights of all the day's action from the fifth round of the FA Cup. In the game of the day, Manchester City will be eager to get revenge for their recent Premier League loss to Chelsea as they entertain Jose Mourinho's side at the Etihad stadium. A revitalised Sunderland take on Mauricio Pochettino's young Southampton side, and holders Wigan will be out to cause another upset as they travel to Cardiff. Commentary from Clive Tyldesley, Joe Speight and Derek Rae.
